    "description": "A strange email from an unknown source... A town with a rich supernatural history.. What mystery awaits to be discovered in the small town of Nightfall Hollow?<br><br>You play as Neo an investigative journalist as you explore the open, living, pixel art town and meet all of its residents.<br>During your investigation you will solve puzzles, Hunt for clues and items to help you, meet and talk to all the residents where your discoveries and choices matter!<br>Can you Solve all the puzzles, find all the hidden clues and get to the truth of the town!<br><br>Nightfall Hollow is a rich story driven game with a paranormal edge. Your choices matter in this game, Residents will remember your dialogue choices and they 'MAY' help you with your investigation or ignore you - depending on what you do! and what you find along the way!<br><br>A lot of love has gone in to the lore of Nightfall Hollow, and we hope you enjoy discovering it<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291740/extras/ac9235193fc50b883ab2f0447262cd8a.avif?t=1690981594\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291740/extras_big/ac9235193fc50b883ab2f0447262cd8a.avif?t=1690981594 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291740/extras/727ca933fd8a62b09070bb14837d29b7.avif?t=1690981594\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291740/extras_big/727ca933fd8a62b09070bb14837d29b7.avif?t=1690981594 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291740/extras/671e5a8bef1a6bf1df776253f24c4bb5.avif?t=1690981594\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291740/